      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Secretary of Health and Human Services, acting through the Commissioner of Food and Drugs, to act upon pending submissions for new infant formula, to increase regulatory flexibility in the event of an infant formula shortage, and for other purposes.</title>
